#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.pad:129
msgid ""
"For an array with rank greater than 1, some of the padding of later axes is "
"calculated from padding of previous axes.  This is easiest to think about "
"with a rank 2 array where the corners of the padded array are calculated by "
"using padded values from the first axis."
